data.description:
This magnificent property features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, and it absolutely a must see. This huge home has
approximately 3,300 square feet of living space, which provides plenty area for the whole family to live comfortably. The
kitchen is stunning in both appearance and performance, making it ideal for hosting gatherings and preparing meals for
family and friends. The use of vinyl plank flooring throughout the house gives it a contemporary appearance and makes it
very easy to keep clean. You'll find a separate bedroom on the upper floor that's both spacious and private, complete with
its own bathroom and balcony and providing a quiet refuge from the rest of the house. Outside, the property is situated on
a little more than a third of an acre, which provides a generous amount of outdoor space that can be used for activities
with the family as well as for hosting guests. When the Florida evenings get cool, gathering around the fire pit in the
backyard to relax and toast marshmallows is the perfect way to spend them. This property is in a desirable community
that features a golf course, and it is conveniently located near a variety of shops and restaurants, making it the ideal spot
to call home. Do not pass up the opportunity to purchase this stunning home in Sebring!
